## Limitations

The findings are based on available online resources and may not encompass all aspects of the issue. The data is primarily from U.S.-based studies and articles, which may not fully represent global perspectives. Additionally, the emotional and social impacts are subjective and can vary widely among individuals. Further research, including interviews and longitudinal studies, would provide a more comprehensive understanding of the challenges faced by women in late-life divorce.